high_descs: Head left to the opposite side of the hall until you reach a kitchen sink.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Walk around the sink to the upper right corner with the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave.
Go back to the position at the sink you came from.
Pick up another potato from next to the sink, on the right.
Head back to the microwave.
Place the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put two pieces of potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Go towards the kitchen area on the left, towards the sink.
Pick up the potato from the sink basin.
Walk around the counters into the kitchen area, to the microwave.
Put the potato into the microwave.
Go back to the sink.
Pick up the potato from the panel next to the sink.
Return to the microwave.
Place the second potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place two Potatoes in a Microwave.

high_descs: Walk move go straight and near to the sink.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Go straight turn right and near to the microwave.
Collect the potato inside the microwave.
Turn around and near to the sink.
Pick up the potato from the sink.
Walk back and near to the microwave.
Collect the potato inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Collect the potato from the sink and keep it inside the microwave.
